gov.nih.nlm.meme.action
Interface BatchAction

All Known Subinterfaces:
BatchAction
All Known Implementing Classes:
BatchMolecularTransaction, MacroMolecularAction
public interface BatchAction

Generically represents a batch action. It provides an API for container classes for the parameters necessary to call MEME_BATCH_ACTIONS.batch_action.

Author:
MEME Group
